            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic in pace iacet Leontius ex optione <lb n="2"/>officio magistri <expan><abbr>eq</abbr><ex>uitum</ex></expan> et peditum quem <lb n="3"/>terra extera duxit qui vixit annus <note>sic</note> XL <lb n="4"/>vitam A&amp;lt;l=N&amp;gt;<expan><abbr>te</abbr><ex>na</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Roma</abbr><ex>na</ex></expan> qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> servivit an<lb break="no" n="5"/>nus <note>sic</note> XVI coniugi caro in qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> arca si <lb n="6"/>quis cum suis &amp;lt;et=TE&amp;gt; Altenam Romanam <lb n="7"/>dederit corpus <expan><abbr>de</abbr><ex>t</ex></expan> <surplus>h</surplus>ec<expan><ex>c</ex><abbr>lesiae</abbr></expan> paenam <note>sic</note> <lb n="8"/>auri pondo duo depositum in die <lb n="9"/>VII Idus Iunias 
            </ab></div>
